SUMMARY:Spring Ladies Night Out at grandview
DESCRIPTION:Join us on Thursday\, March 26th at Grandview Vineyard for a Ladies Night Out starting at 5:30pm! Celebrate Spring being right around the corner with a night out with all your friends.\nJoining us for the evening:Adorned Tattoos providing fine line tattoos – sign up sheet that nightL2 Permanent JewelryHair tinsel by KatieMama B SweetsBeauty Co providing eyebrow shading and more!\n\nWe will be serving our wine & cocktails all night. Event is free to attend and individual activity pricing will vary.\nTime: 5:30pm – 8:30pm
URL:https://grandviewwines.com/vineyard-event/spring-ladies-night-out-at-grandview-3/
LOCATION:Grandview Vineyard\, 1489 Grandview Rd\, Mount Joy\, PA\, 17552\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://grandviewwines.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Ladies-Night-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
